#      - Ensure POLYGON_API_KEY is set in your .env file
#      - Check that your .env file is in the correct directory

# ❌ 2. "OpenAI API error" messages:
#      - Verify your OPENAI_API_KEY is correct
#      - Check your OpenAI account has sufficient credits
#      - Ensure you have access to the specified model

# ❌ 3. "uvx not found" error:
#      - Install uvx: pip install uvx
#      - Ensure uvx is available in your PATH

# ❌ 4. Port already in use:
#      - Change FASTAPI_PORT to a different port (e.g., 8001)
#      - Or stop the process using the port

# ❌ 5. CORS errors in frontend:
#      - Check that your React dev server port matches CORS origins
#      - Add additional origins if needed in CORS_ORIGINS

